venv\Scripts\activate

# On macOS/Linux
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
```

3. **Install required packages:**
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Or install manually:
```bash
pip install numpy pandas matplotlib scikit-learn jupyter
```

